metadata.name: Elegant
metadata.description:
Elegant - Bstract x Lashbat

“Elegance is the only beauty that never fades.” – Audrey Hepburn.

This is a collection of art combining the work of NFT artist Bstract and Lashbat (Evie)
Evie is Bstract's first artist part of his onboarding initiative, the majority of the sale will be going to Evie to get her started in the NFT space.
Bstracts - https://linktr.ee/Bstract
Lashbat - https://www.instagram.com/lashbat/
